<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-research-improves-dense-breast-cancer-screening-and-early-detection/">Mayo Clinic research improves dense breast cancer screening and early detection</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
